 8 dice.
 In general, for 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

-again, the average number of successes rolled per die is 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{3}{n-1}$
\end_inset

.
 Furthermore, it doesn't help at all when you only care if you succeed or
